<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <title>Siker!</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="5;url=/dashboard" /> </head>
<body class="bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center h-screen text-center p-4">
    <div>
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-6xl mb-4 animate-bounce"></i>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase mb-2">Fizetés Sikeres!</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">A rendszer automatikusan aktiválta a licencet.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 inline-block text-left">
            <p>Csomag: <strong class="text-purple-400"><%= plan %></strong></p>
            <p>Lejárat: <strong class="text-white"><%= date %></strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mt-8">Visszairányítás a Dashboardra 5 másodpercen belül...</p>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="block mt-4 bg-white text-black font-bold py-2 rounded">Azonnali belépés</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>